ufficient technical competence and acceptable crew interaction. Candidate\u202fB uniquely combines proven reliability and calmness, with adequate technical skills, making the candidate the most robust overall fit despite the noted interpersonal weaknesses.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fB\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
